This analysis is based on Chapter One of the MrP tutorial,

https://bookdown.org/jl5522/MRP-case-studies/

The github repo is here:
https://github.com/JuanLopezMartin/MRPCaseStudy

The needed data for the present analysis can be downloaded here:
https://github.com/JuanLopezMartin/MRPCaseStudy/tree/master/data_public/chapter1/data


You need to download the files

`cces18_common_vv.csv`
`statelevel_predictors.csv`
`poststrat_df.csv`

...and save them in the current directory.

